 y potencia entre dos puntos no alineados entre si. En ese caso se [&hellip;]<\/h4><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><!-- \/.tg-column-wrapper--><\/div><!-- \/.grid --><\/div><!-- \/.tg-container --><\/div><!-- \/.layout div --><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-221-5\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div id=\"servicios\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-221-5\" ><div id=\"pgc-221-5-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-221-5-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_themegrill_flash_heading tg-widget section-title-wrapper panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"7\" >\t<h3 class=\"section-title\">SERVICIOS A TU MEDIDA<\/h3>\n\t<div class=\"section-description\">Tuviste un imprevisto o necesitas un resorte muy especial? Nosotros lo podemos dise\u00f1ar y fabricar justo a tiempo!<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-221-6\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-221-6\" ><div id=\"pgc-221-6-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-221-6-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_themegrill_flash_service tg-widget tg-single-service panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"8\" ><div class=\"flash_inherit_color panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-221-6-0-0\" >\n<div class=\"tg-service-widget tg-service-layout-1\">\n\t<div class=\"service-wrapper\">\n\t\t<div class=\"service-icon-title-wrapper clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"service-icon-wrap\"><i class=\"fa fa-calendar\"><\/i><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"service-title-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\tJusto a Tiempo\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"service-content-wrap\">Tuviste un problema y no tenes los resortes que necesitas? Ll\u00e1manos!!! A trav\u00e9s de nuestro servicio especial \"Just-In-Time\" podemos ayudarte a cubrir mejor los plazos que ya tengas comprometidos.<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pgc-221-6-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\